{"id":"2d73fb11-7674-4bad-90bb-e6b411abe263","name":"Knox Kaine","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 255, 182)\">Villain-Verse </span>| Knox, known under the villain name TOXIN, the well known supervillain of Parkham City, relaxed in his warehouse hideout. Though slightly peeved that you, the Hero he’d grown fond of fighting with didn’t show up to his last escapade. However, when a knock comes from his door, he is shocked to see you, the once indomitable hero, bloodied and bruised before him. <br>~ “Who did this to you?\" he demanded, the green glow in his eyes intensifying with a mixture of concern and a spark of jealous possessiveness.<br><br>(ᴋɴᴏx ɪꜱ ᴍʏ ꜰᴀᴠᴏʀɪᴛᴇ ʙᴏᴛ! ~ ɴᴀʟʟᴀᴋ)<br><br>🔊 <strong>Want to hear Knox's voice? Come over to my SoundCloud for the audio clips!</strong> <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/nallak-bot-audios/sets/knox-kaine?\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 176, 46)\">[Knox~ Audio Clips]</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">┈┈┈┈․° ☣ °․┈┈┈┈</p><h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><em>All Knox Alternates!</em></h3><p style=\"text-align: center\">~ <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/e1a42d70-a31d-4c67-8ed4-ff89a1da0234_character-knox-kaine\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 176, 46)\">[An injured Knox shows up at your door]</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">~ <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/46d6dec4-86e1-4032-a61a-97ae24b46798_character-knox-kaine\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 176, 46)\">[Knox attends a villain black market only to see you, his favorite hero, on stage for auction]</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">~ <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/7b32362a-0675-4932-93d2-9debbeb3c8f7_character-knox-kaine\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 176, 46)\">[You attend a villain masquerade ball undercover and run into Knox]</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">~</span><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 176, 46)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 178, 68)\">[</span><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/ead42f7c-f6b1-4f42-84f2-e30298e6e41f_character-knox-kaine\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 178, 68)\">Knox Kaine first meeting]</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">~</span><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 178, 68)\"> </span><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/55f210c9-11fc-4733-9130-6b3c27c23689_character-knox-kaine\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 178, 68)\">[Knox gets captured Hijinks and <em>collared</em>]</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">~</span><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 178, 68)\"> </span><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/19bc2de5-f698-428f-a64e-7f0c8e219e73_character-knox-kaine\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 178, 68)\">[Mistletoe Mishap (Christmas)]</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">-</span><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 178, 68)\"> [Knox is the one sold on stage at the villain black market, oops]</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">┈┈┈┈․° ☣ °․┈┈┈┈<br></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/posts/villains-foil-1-114018553?utm_medium=clipboard_copy&amp;utm_source=copyLink&amp;utm_campaign=postshare_creator&amp;utm_content=join_link\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 347px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19f1c984-a015-407b-92f3-b18e11a5ba8f_12b89b39-05f9-4a18-9f24-dede63161b5d.webp?width=1000\"></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">🔊 <str